<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Glee Tours and Travels</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="screen" href= "/public/assets/css/home.css"/>

    <%- include('partials/head') %>

    <header class="background" style="background-image: url('/public/assets/images/flag.webp');">
        <div class="headerTitle">
            <h1 style="font-size: 40px;" id="headerh1">Explore Pakistan with us</h1>
            <img src="/public/assets/images/dots-3.png" alt="dots">
            <p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; " id="headerP">Welcome to Glee Tours and Travels
            </p>
            <span><a href="/admin/view-tours">Admin Panel</a></span>
            <a href="#intro" class="downArrowCircle">
                <i id="scrollDownBtn" class="fa fa-3x fa-angle-down" style="color: rgb(195, 33, 33)"></i>
            </a>
    </header>
    <div class="intro" id="intro">
        <div class="introLeft">
            <img src="/public/assets/images/samaan.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="introRight">
            <h1 >START YOUR
                <strong style="color: rgb(195, 33, 33);">JOURNEY</strong> TODAY</h1>
            <p>Pakistan is richly known for its fascinating tourist attractions. Northern areas of Pakistan offer such breathtaking
                sceneries that tourists from all over Pakistan visit them throughout summer season. Apart from northern areas,
                Pakistan is home to stunning beaches as well as scenic deserts. The traditional, cultural and religious attractions are spread
                throughout Pakistan and are worth the visit. Glee Tours and Travels is a travel agency making journeys all
                over Pakistan. We offer both standard and custom tours as per the demand of our clients. We guarantee complete
                satsfaction to our clients who want to explore this beautiful country.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="scrollToDiv" style="position: relative; bottom: 60px;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="introCards introCardsBackground" style="background-image: url(/public/assets/images/slider-bg.jpg);">
        <div class="introCard">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            <h3>About Us</h3>
            <p>
                We are group of young enthusiastic professionals who understand the tourism industry and want to provide the people of Pakistan
                quality tourism services. We have been organizing successful journeys for a considerable length of time through
                our exceptionally curated tour packages and high quality services.
        </div>
        <div class="introCard">
            <i class="far fa-compass"></i>
            <h3>Services</h3>
            <p>We offer different plans according to your need. Our plans include custom tours, group tours, family tours, trekking
                tours and honeymoon tours. The services include hotel reservation, private transport, guide and other services
                according to the plan. We try to ensure that your travel experience with us is as satisfying as possible.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="introCard">
            <i class="far fa-check-circle"></i>
            <h3>Why Us</h3>
            <p>We, at Glee Tours and Travels, believe in rendering high quality tourism services within Pakistan. Client satisfaction
                is our top priority. We make sure that your journeys are always safe and enjoyable. Having completed many
                successful tours across Pakistan, we can guarantee that your journey with us will be memorable.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="toursDiv">
        <div class="toursDivLeft">
            <img src="/public/assets/images/family_tour3.jpg" alt="Family Tours">
        </div>
        <div class="toursDivRight">
            <div>
                <h2>FAMILY TOURS</h2>
                <p>
                    Glee tours and travels offers customized family tours to help you visit all of the dream places you wished to visit with your 
                    family. Our family tours are luxurious, safe and cover every destination you want to visit. Make yours trips the most memorable 
                    by travelling with your family. Family tours also include honeymoon tours which are affordable and allow you to spend quality time
                    with your other half.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="toursDiv">
        <div class="toursDivLeft">
            <img src="/public/assets/images/group-tours.jpeg" alt="Group Tours">
        </div>
        <div class="toursDivRight2">
            <div>
                <h2>GROUP TOURS</h2>
                <p>
                    Glee tours and travels welcomes you to join our group tours in which we travel in the form of groups. We leave every week 
                    for different destinations and give you opportunity to make your trips memorable by travelling together. Group tours include
                    adventure tours, cultural tours, religious tours and regional tours. Be ready for our next group tour and don't miss the
                    amazing experience of travelling together.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="toursDiv">
        <div class="toursDivLeft">
            <img src="/public/assets/images/custom_tours2.jpg" alt="Family Tours">
        </div>
        <div class="toursDivRight">
            <div>
                <h2>CUSTOM TOURS</h2>
                <p>
                    We offer you the ability to customize your tours so that the trip includes everything you want. You can choose the destinations of
                    your choice along with the services that you need. These tours can range from basic to luxurious according to your custom plan. Whether
                    you are travelling alone or with a group of family or friends, we can make tailor-made trips for you. 
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="heading">
        <h1>UPCOMING TOURS</h1>
    </div>
    <ul class="toursDetailsList">
        <% tours.reverse() %>
        <% let count = 0 %>
        <% for(let tour of tours) { count+=1; if(count===4){break;} %>
        <li class="toursDetailsCard">
            <div class="toursDetailsCardImgDiv">
                <img src="/public/assets/images/<%=tour.image.filename%>" alt="Skardu Tour">
                <div><%= tour.days %> <% if( tour.days > 1 ) { %> Days Tour <% } else{ %> Day Tour <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="toursDetailsCardTextDiv">
                <h2>
                    <%= tour.title %>
                </h2>
                <div>
                    <% if(tour.packageInclusion) { %>
                    <a href="/tour-details/<%=tour._id%>"><button class="detailsBtn detailsBtnTransition">View Details</button></a>
                    <% } %>
                    <a href="/contact-us"><button class="bookNowBtn bookNowBtnTransition">Book Now</button></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <% } %> 
    </ul>

    <div class="viewAllDiv">
        <div>
            <a class="button" href="/tours">
                <span>View All</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Starting of Slider -->
    <div id="slidy-container-div" class="sliderBackground" style="background-image: url(/public/assets/images/slider-bg2.jpg);">
        <h1 class="heading2">MEMORABLE JOURNEYS</h1>
        <div id="slidy-container">
            <figure id="slidy">
                <img src="/public/assets/images/2.jpg" alt="eyes">
                <img src="/public/assets/images/14.jpg" alt="lou">
                <img src="/public/assets/images/16.jpg" alt="lou">
                <img src="/public/assets/images/17.jpg" alt="lucie-2">
                <img src="/public/assets/images/12.jpg" alt="lucie">
                <img src="/public/assets/images/3.jpg" alt="lucie">

            </figure>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Ending of Slider -->


    <img class="footerTopImg" style="display: block;" src="/public/assets/images/wave3.svg" alt="">
    <footer>
        <img src="/public/assets/images/logo.png">
        <!--<p>Copyright &#169; 2022 Glee Tours and Travels</p>-->
        <div>
            <h2>
                <p>FOLLOW US</p>
                <p>
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/gleetours.pk"><i class="fab fa-facebook" style="text-decoration: none; color: white;"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://instagram.com/gleetours.pk?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y="><i class="fab fa-instagram" style="text-decoration: none; color: white;"></i></a>
                </p>
            </h2>
            <h2>
                <p>CONTACT US</p>
                <p>
                    <i class='fa fa-phone'></i>
                    <span>03000233669</span>
                </p>
            </h2>
        </div>

    </footer>



    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js " integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo "
        crossorigin="anonymous "></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.14.7/dist/umd/popper.min.js " integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1 "
        crossorigin="anonymous "></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js " integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM "
        crossorigin="anonymous "></script>
    <script src="/public/assets/js/home.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
